      <div class="w-full max-w-3xl rounded-2xl border border-white/40 bg-white/50 p-6 shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm dark:border-slate-700/40 dark:bg-slate-900/50 sm:p-8">
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">Quick Summary</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-base text-secondary-foreground">
          <p>
            Senior Machine Learning Engineer with 12+ years of experience across the full ML lifecycle‚Äîfrom designing custom GPU kernels and distributed training frameworks to deploying multi-modal GenAI models.
