          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div>
              <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-foreground">Current Role</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-secondary-foreground">Senior ML Engineer @ Adobe</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-secondary-foreground opacity-75">Jan 2024 - Present</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-foreground">Education</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-secondary-foreground">Ph.D. in Computer Science</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-secondary-foreground opacity-75">The Ohio State University</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full max-w-3xl rounded-2xl border border-white/40 bg-white/50 p-6 shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm dark:border-slate-700/40 dark:bg-slate-900/50 sm:p-8">
